data.title: Former Senate President Stan Rosenberg Resigns
data.meta_description: Senator Stan Rosenberg, former Massachusetts Senate President, submitted his official resignation today in the wake of mounting calls for him to step down.
data.text:
Former Massachusetts Senate President Stan Rosenberg officially submitted his letter of resignation today, effective Friday at 5pm. Rosenberg was facing mounting calls for him to step down from members of both parties in the wake of yesterday's ethics report.

Guests

Steve Brown, WBUR reporter. Steve tweets @wbursteve.
